It was built in 2017 and features approximately 14,207 square feet of living space with 4 bedrooms, 9 bathrooms, foyer with floating staircase & glass elevator, 2-story great room, living room with wet bar, dining room, gourmet kitchen, office, game room with wet bar, home theater, gym, lounge with indoor rock climbing wall, wine cellar, indoor half-court basketball court, 12-car garage with lift to the master suite and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, motor court, multiple balconies/patios, kitchen/BBQ, wet bar, infinity pool, spa, water & fire features and a putting green.

It's listed at $32,500,000

Good morning! 😍 This French inspired limestone home, dubbed “Chateau de la Roche”, is located at 48 Rio Vista Drive, Alpine, New Jersey and is situated on 2 acres of land.

It was designed by Zampolin & Associates and built in 2017. It features approximately 25,700 square feet of living space with 7 bedrooms, 12 bathrooms, 2-story foyer with double staircase, elevator, 2-story great room, formal dining room, gourmet kitchen with double islands, breakfast room, family room, 2-story conservatory, paneled home office/library, 15-seat home theater, billiards room, 2 wet bars, wine cellar, 2 indoor plunge pools, sauna, steam room, garage and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, balcony, patio, gazebo with BBQ/kitchen, swimming pool with spa, pool house and a fountain.

It's listed at $25,000,000

It was designed by Richard Drummond Davis and built in 2014. 

It features approximately 16,679 square feet of living space with 5 bedrooms, 5 full and 3 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with floating staircase, great room, formal dining room, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, family room, paneled library, paneled office, paneled billiards room, paneled media room with wet bar, 10-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, motor court, covered patio with fireplace, swimming pool with spa, cabana with 2nd fireplace and a putting green.

It sold on 06/11/20 after being listed at $10,500,000
